scene.message:
Queen: Ugh, honestly!{nl}
Another mole popped up!{waitkey}{clearbox}This mirror's handy, but{nl}
one wish and the moles{nl}
multiply like this? A scam!{waitkey}{ret}

Queen: ...{wait_fr:32}So you've come!{nl}
Well? My painting was{nl}
the better one, wasn't it?!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Chisato...{wait_fr:48} please,{nl}
stop this now...{waitkey}{clearbox}I already know your{nl}
painting's better...{wait_fr:48}{nl}
And those moles...{waitkey}{ret}

Queen: Oh, shut up!{nl}
Don't say things{nl}
you don't even mean!{waitkey}{clearbox}You think I got what{nl}
I deserved, don't you!{waitkey}{ret}

Queen: Never mind that.{nl}
{ctl0f:1}, there's something{nl}
I want to show you.{waitkey}{ret}

Queen: Hey, {ctl0f:1},{nl}
you saw the paintings hung{nl}
in the exhibition room?{waitkey}{clearbox}My painting, and this{nl}
miserable painting of Maki's -{nl}
which do you think is better?{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Sonomura's painting{nl}
is obviously the better{nl}
one, duhhh!{waitkey}{ret}

Queen: Mirror, mirror,{nl}
grant Chisato's wish!{waitkey}{clearbox}Turn those monkeys{wait_fr:32}{nl}
into stone!{nl}
Nomoraka tanomamaa!{waitkey}{ret}

Queen: Ah-hahahaha!!{nl}
Turn to stone, just like that!{wait_fr:64}{nl}
...Ah!{waitkey}{ret}

Queen: Daaamn it!{nl}
Another mole popped up{nl}
again!{waitkey}{clearbox}Turning you to stone was{nl}
too soft! I should've put{nl}
you through something worse!{waitkey}{ret}

Queen: {ctl0f:1},{nl}
I'll give you, and only you,{nl}
a chance.{waitkey}{clearbox}My beautiful painting,{nl}
and Maki's painting -{nl}
which do you think is better?{waitkey}Now, answer me honestly!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: You idiot!{nl}
Do you really think{nl}
that's true?!{waitkey}{ret}

Queen: Hehehe, ah-hahaha!{waitkey}{clearbox}How about that, Maki!{nl}
{ctl0f:1} chose me{nl}
over you.{waitkey}{ret}

Aki: Honestly, what are you{nl}
doing, Queen!{waitkey}{clearbox}I told you to beat{nl}
these guys!{waitkey}{ret}

Queen: I'm sorry, Angel.{nl}
But if I get any more{nl}
moles than this...{waitkey}{ret}

Aki: Then if you beat them,{nl}
I'll put your face{nl}
back to normal!{waitkey}{ret}

Queen: You promise?!{wait_fr:48}{nl}
...All right.{nl}
I'll do it!{waitkey}{ret}

Queen: I'm sorry, {ctl0f:1}.{nl}
You're actually pretty{nl}
much my type, but...{waitkey}{ret}

Queen: Mirror, mirror,{nl}
hear Chisato's wish.{nl}
Grant me power!{waitkey}Nomoraka tanomamaa!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Serves you right!{nl}
This guy's no coward who'd{nl}
cave to threats!{waitkey}{clearbox}...Ngh!{waitkey}{ret}

Queen: {ctl0f:1},{waitkey}I thought you of all people{nl}
would understand, but{nl}
I misjudged you.{waitkey}{clearbox}I'll repay this humiliation{nl}
tenfold!{wait_fr:48} Turn to stone{nl}
with the rest of them!{waitkey}{ret}

Aki: Ugh, you're still at it?{waitkey}Hey, Queen, if you beat{nl}
these guys, I'll put your{nl}
face back to normal!{waitkey}{ret}

Queen: Since the Angel{nl}
says so, change of plans.{waitkey}{clearbox}I'll defeat you all{nl}
with my own hands!{waitkey}{ret}

Naito: ...{wait_fr:48}Silly Chisato.{nl}
Have a little more faith{nl}
in me, won't you?{waitkey}{ret}

Kozai: But, Yosuke,{nl}
I was so anxious.{waitkey}{clearbox}I kept worrying about{nl}
what I'd do if you{nl}
came to hate me.{waitkey}{ret}

Naito: Haha, you!{nl}
As if I could ever{nl}
come to hate you, Chisato.{waitkey}{clearbox}Don't make such a sad{nl}
face. Smile for me,{wait_fr:48}{nl}
all right, Chii dear?{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: {wait_fr:48}'Chii dear,'{wait_fr:48} he says...{wait_fr:48}{nl}
Looks like we're in{nl}
the way. Let's head out,{nl}
{ctl0f:1}...{waitkey}{ret}
